Class GUIView

  • java.lang.Object
    • it.polimi.se2019.util.Observable

  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    public class GUIView
extends View
    The GUIView class is an extension of the abstract View class. It implements the methods of the View for input buidling and view selection for the gui application.
